<br>
The ONLY other time I pped was when I was grouped with me, enchanter, and druid and they asked me to taunt the mobs before breaking the mes.  Backstab by itself wasn't cutting it, so I'd pp the monster twice and then backstab, which usually was enough to draw aggro.  They didn't seem to mind, as it was Orcs in Highpass and they were twinks they didn't care much about the few GP i looted anyway.<br>
